00:01:01.025 --> 00:01:05.024
the exposure is the amount of light that reaches the camera sensor

00:01:05.024 --> 00:01:07.024
let's leave it zero for now

00:01:10.827 --> 00:01:12.827
now let's change the shutter speed

00:01:13.107 --> 00:01:15.107
