00:01:31.468 --> 00:01:34.709
and it's the third factor with the shutter speed and apreture

00:01:34.709 --> 00:01:37.109
in determining the exposure of the image

00:01:37.483 --> 00:01:39.901
the lower the ISO, the lower the amount of light reaching the sensor

00:01:39.901 --> 00:01:41.900
and the image will be sharp

00:01:42.200 --> 00:01:44.602
and the higher the ISO, the greater the light will reach the sensor

00:01:44.602 --> 00:01:46.434
and the image becomes noisy

00:01:46.434 --> 00:01:49.130
therefore we choose the ISO 100

00:01:49.317 --> 00:01:52.320
